/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the cityscape. The street is flanked by tall buildings, their facades painted in shades of beige and brown, reflecting the urban architecture of the city. The sky above is overcast, casting a soft, diffused light over the scene. The street itself is lined with trees, their green foliage adding a touch of nature to the concrete jungle. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in many cities. The image is slightly distorted due to the fisheye lens effect, adding a unique perspective to the urban landscape.
